Package: crateos
Version: 0.1.0+noble1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: CrateOS <crateos@localhost>
Description: CrateOS framework console and runtime identity
 Interactive console, login/runtime branding, and CLI for the CrateOS server framework.
 Provides the 'crateos' command with console, status, and version subcommands.
 Establishes CrateOS as an Ubuntu 24.04 (noble) derived operator surface.
Depends: openssh-server, dos2unix
